quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  35,31,"Kon ko Men wahayini e maa…óa e Deftere nden, ko …óum woni goonga, gom…óinde e …óen won…óe yeeso mayre. Pellet, Alla ko Humpitii…óo Rentu…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen"
  35,32,"Refti Men ronini Deftere nden, …ďen …ďe Men su…ďii e jeyaa…ďe Amen. Hino e ma…ď…ďe too√Īu…ďe hoore-mun, hino e ma…ď…ďe hakindin…óo, hino e ma…ď…ďe foolondiroo…ďe e mo∆ī∆īereeji, duŇčayee Alla; ko …óum woni …ďural mawnungal ngal"
  35,33,"Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal, …ói naatata e mun, hara hi…ďe cu…óiree ton, jawe kaŇčŇče e kaalise e lu‚Äôu-lu‚Äôu; comci ma…ď…ďe …óin ton, ko sooyi"
  35,34,"∆Āe wi'a: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On ittan…óo en suno. Pellet, Joomi men, ko Haforoowo, Warjotoo…óo"
  35,35,"On weernir…óo en …ďural Makko ngal, e galle √Īii…ďal, tampere (woo) he…ďataa en ton, wanaa ronkere he…ďata en ton"
  35,36,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen kan, ko Yiite Jahannama woodani …ďen; maayde √Īaawetaake e ma…ď…ďe, sakko …ďe maaya, …ďe hoynantaake kadi lepte magge …óen. Ko wano nii Men yo…ďitirta kala yeddu…óo"
  35,37,"Hara hi…ďe ooloo nder ton […ďe wi'a]: \"Joomi amen, yaltin men; men golla mo∆ī∆īere, hara wonah ko men gollaynoo kon\". [O jaaboo …ďe]: \"E men wuurnaano on yeru ko waajitotoo…óo waajitoranoo e mun? Jertinoowo kadi ari e mon? Awa mee…óee, sabu faabo alanaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  35,38,"Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo wirnii…ói kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Ko O Anndu…óo ko suu…óii e …ďer…óe"
